Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in Okinawa Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An interview between Uncle and a baseball\Nplayer becomes a murder mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks like a child but has the brain of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed one bit, Nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still have the habit of leaning your head\Ntowards the right side when you're running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mo... Motoyama. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only a bit after 9:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you on the phone last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as it's for you... I'd fly aver right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Hideyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Course Without Protest. (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a day before Tokyo{zamanlama yap}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You're going to Okinawa tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I hear anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? I thought you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The professional baseball team the\NJaguars' MVP, Nose Toshizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:03:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nichiuri TV arranged for me to talk\Nwith Nose-senshu face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did they pick you, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A professional baseball player and a detective\Ndon't have too much in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose-senshu is one of few pitchers in pro-baseball\Nwho plays the game using his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll use his ability to see through his opponents hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To challenge my deduction skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But can you successfully talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose-senshu is famous for being hard to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sports reporter who has a good relationship\Nwith Nose-senshu will also be joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here in Miyazaki with Kogure-senshu\Nwho's doing some independent training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To increase the Falcons' chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can feel the determination oozing from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will be talking with\NNose-senshu tomorrow in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hope that it'll be just as interesting as today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and I are good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we'll also be joined by the famous\Ndetective Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When's your flight tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be leaving from Haneda airport\Nat 6:35 tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Nose-senshu only has the\Nmorning free in his busy schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Doesn't that mean that we'll\Nhave to wake up before five?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we should get prepared and\Ngo to sleep early too, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... I'm the only one who's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's use this time to go buy something\Nfrom the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to hurry or we won't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all because Dad didn't tell us earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's being mean, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heeeeeeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same Day Miyazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nose. Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My interview that just ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:52.19,Signs,,0,0,0,,Motoyama Masaharu\NSports Reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:50.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, the on Nichiuri TV night news
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Sports Corner segment that starts at 6:30, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same Time Okinawa{Tag at}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I just happened to be out eating and didn't catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:04.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nose Toshizou\NPro Baseball Player
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:03.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm just about to go train with some younger\Nplayers and probably have a few drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Was there something you needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really. I just wanted to thank you in advance for tomorrow's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should thank you for covering for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In case Mouri Kogorou asks any strange questions,\Nplease follow up well to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be late for your flight tomorrow, Motoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were never very good at waking up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. My Flight's at 8:15 tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as it's for you... I'd fly over right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Hideyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm Nobunago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that it was me who introduced you to the\Ntelevision aspect of sports after you retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's because we were on the same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to keep such a small favor on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the younger players are calling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't drink too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a chance of breaking the Japanese\Nrecord with your games so for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nobunaga" you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're more like Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Number 931 (Tokyo Okinawa){tag at}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still tugged alone in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We called the people at the TV station last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't they agree to pay for both me and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all because of you guys that my status\Nwas downgraded to economy class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Okinawan food was great that last time we went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drinking and partying with beautiful Okinawan women...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My perfect plan is... Completely ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll only take a few pictures with the digital\Ncamera. We won't interfere with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? You got a digital camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the one Dad won in the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I' m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring tennis balls along?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boys from our school baseball team\Ncalled lost night after watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wanted me to ask for some Nose-senshu's autography.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told them that we didn't have any nice paper for\Nautographs, but they said that anything would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I brought along some tennis balls that Sonoko gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the baseball you had was all covered in mud, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bringing four balls means that there's\Nfour baseball players in your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, only three are in the baseball\Nclub. The other one's for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's for Eri, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a Jaguar fan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. So please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you please get mom's as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asking a professional baseball player\Nto autograph a tennis ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to do something so embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okinawa (Naha Airport){tag at}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Teranishi from Okinowa's Nichiuri TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of my\Ndaughter and him as well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your daughter? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you guys going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to see if I can buy some autograph paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way what, happened to what\Nwe spoke about lost time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that one at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already reserved some seats at a very nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no... I'm afraid we'll have to cancel that tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was actually asking about that other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've asked our guest Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And have gotten it quite successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which... Is Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nalready here from Miyazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet. His plane won't be here until 9:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still have to wait 30 more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the only plane that goes from Miyazaki to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could you take us to the hotel where\Nwe'll be interviewing Nose-senshu first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a problem... But even if you go,\NNose-senshu isn't there yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every morning between 9 o'clock and 10\No'clock is when he does his jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably... Jogging somewhere\Naround the hotel right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okinawa (Naha City){tag at}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi's counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What he did to Mitsuhide who killed\NNobunaga to take over the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rushing from Okayama to Kyouto in only three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Counterattacks have always been Hideyoshi's best skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't let you have this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okinawa (Naha Airport){tag at}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how long are you going to look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} plane should be here anytime now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no autograph paper anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help you get your friends those autographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Mom's too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know anywhere around here\Nthat sells autograph paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Autograph paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. The closest one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C mon, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah. He's here! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. This way, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you all wait so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you. I'm detective Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Motoyama Masaharu. I've heard\Nabout you from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's finish the introductions in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okinawa is so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with this rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're going, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} looks really easy to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he can help me get Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Nose hasn't returned to the hotel yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he got tired while jogging and took\Na rest somewhere. He's getting a little old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get a cold if you sleep there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That' s...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Jaguar uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on... Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't that Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the ambulance and the police fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The police?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't that Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the ambulance and the police fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The police?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. There's no use calling for on ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s already died from a stab wound in his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, you've got the digital camera right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take pictures of the scene of the\Ncrime before the police come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... Digital camera, digital camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find it yet, Ran? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take two or three pictures from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to step in the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to bring Mom some pictures of\NNose-senshu in this signature poses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now I'm taking this kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do it. You can go back to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this Nose from the Jaguars?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard on TV that he was doing independent training here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time at death is around 9:30 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cause off death is excessive blood loss due\Nto the stub wound on the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it looks like we haven't found the murder weapon yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who discovered the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who discovered the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our car just happened to pass by this area\Nand found Nose-senshu lying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably attacked while jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're very famous in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard that you can eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because of Uncle and Hattori's\Neating contest in Okinawa lust time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, the case is just like it's already solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do these guys really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I know someone who's better than Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sports reporter Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when we first saw Nose-senshu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain had already washed the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't get close and look carefully enough, you'd\Nnever notice that he'd been stabbed in his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And for someone who knew about Nose-son's jogging
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't they usually think that Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwas sick and had collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hadn't even left the car, but you\Ntold us to call the police anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the ambulance and the police fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That deduction is even better than Holmes could have made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know? That this is a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I do remember you saying that\Nbefore I even saw Nose-son's stab wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was that phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I finished taping yesterday's show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I culled Nose from the Miyazaki hotel and he told me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That some anti-Jaguar mun had\Nbeen harassing him by phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was very angry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when I saw Nose lying there, my mind immediately\Nconnected the two things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you guys suspect me, you're\Njust wasting your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have committed this crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of Nose's estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it this morning around 9:30?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just leaving from Miyazaki at 8:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was on the plane that arrived in Okinawa at 9:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check the passenger list.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on... My name isn't on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit of a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want people to notice me, so I always\Nbuy tickets under another name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put on a hat to mask myself\Nso people won't recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what's your nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... It's Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I think it was Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if we can prove that Motoyama was in Miyazaki\Nyesterday night, then the alibi is solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because this is the only flight between\NMiyazaki and Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's what you need, then just ask that hotel I stayed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Miyazaki Princess Hotel's... The room number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used the hotel's phone to call Nose's cellphone last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be able to find it in the hotel's calling record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. Go confirm that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have to ask everyone to accompany\Nme to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Just when we finally get to have an interview...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's from Okinawa's Nichiuri TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were actually supposed to tape\Nan interview with Nose-senshu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the three of us, including Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But suddenly on the way to his hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered Nose's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll get detailed information after we get to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! We also found this on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A schedule and o cardboard tennis ball box?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! It probably fell out when\NI was getting out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okinawa Providence Police Naha Headquarters{tag at}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we've confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hotel call record.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} called from 19:20 to 19:23.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So his calling Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from Miyazaki.\NHotel should be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:20:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I didn't have that, yesterday evening,\NI was live on TV in Miyazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Viewers across the country can prove my alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, did you ask him what the threatener\Nharassing Nose-senshu looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I know is that it was a strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also checked with his other teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't hear anything about harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose is the guardian of the Jaguars.\NHe could score the fear out of child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he wouldn't tell other people\Nthat he was being harassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told me because we have a very\Ndeep, long-lasting friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it... Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and\NNose-senshu joined the team at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even got the rookie MVP title in your first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my shoulder was injured in the second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was never able to return to my original status\Nafter the operation, so I retired in my fifth year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost to the "Second Year Jinx."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That turned out to be just a dream over night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell Nose this while in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to the young players doing independent training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like it is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should cancel tomorrow's\Ninterview with the younger players.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway... Please catch that murderer as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The monster who destroyed my friend's dream\Nof beating Japan's notional record.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man is the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I make a phone call? I'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he has an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:21:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the wind I sometimes smile, sometimes cry, and sometimes fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:23:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us are just like this standing in front of our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our dream is sure to be somewhere in the unknown future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The colors of the seasons, always repeating let us experience a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look upon the side of your sleepy face with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Staying in that moment, this becomes our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:30.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.10,0:24:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just had a scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.91,0:24:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an empty space, but you can't head in directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: A Course Without Protest (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.78,0:24:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Canon's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.69,0:24:51.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.09,0:24:53.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Signs}-kun{\r}, how are you doing with your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.04,0:24:54.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Will Shinichi be okay?
